name: Cadaveric Incubator of Endoparasites (Cadaver for short)
description: This map originally started as an outlet for my flesh texture fetish: I always felt that the flesh textures were a bit underused in this day and age, so I decided to go a bit overboard. About partway through I decided to throw a DeHackEd patch in to spice things up: it doesn't change things too much, but keep on your toes. :-)
